    "SDK capability promoted without exact semantic capability",
    "host-language product body created",
    "temp builder used",
    "resolver or node_modules patched",
    "durable product truth accepted"
  ],
  "completionPosture": "The SDK capability forge can fail closed on exact semantic capability gaps and emit the next governed conveyor story."
